  <brief_title>Phase 2 Study of EPI-743 in Children With Pearson Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open-Label Phase 2 Safety and Efficacy Study of EPI-743 (VincerinoneTM) in Children With Pearson Syndrome</official_title>
