      Treatment of Pediatric Subjects with Pearson syndrome
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      If effective, treatment with EPI-743 should result in a significant reduction in occurrence
      of sepsis, metabolic crisis, hepatic failure and transfusion dependence.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
